{"tid":2118824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國眾議院通過法案 政府雇員、國會議員禁用公務機下載TikTok","createTime":"2020-07-21T17:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T18:23:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c2bc933f6be42cb5fb312e4706b9b9ad763054d5","tid":2118824,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"據美國媒體 The Politico 報導，這項提案作為《國防授權法案》（ National Defense Authorization Act ）修正案的一部分，由共和黨眾議員巴克（ Ken Buck ）提出，於當地時間星期一以 336 票同意、 71 票反對通過，不只聯邦雇員禁用 TikTok ，包括國會議員和員工也受此法規範。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾議院將在週二（ 21 ）通過眾院版本的《國防授權法案》，參議院也會在本週通過參院版的法案，之後會在聯合協調委員會中就法案分歧的部份進行協商。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wealth.com.tw/home/articles/26659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wealth.com.tw%2Fhome%2Farticles%2F26659&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=96943574\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wealth.com.tw/home/articles/26659</a>"},{"pid":"400820af57a635789b7b5443a51981427d09a980","tid":2118824,"uid":95138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T17:07:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"862506ea003bfa9d1b00b7c2b0aaee4d78d96b68","tid":2118824,"uid":270220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"邊71個共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1439e83aff1eb6286a6190c5f481e307958c8915","tid":2118824,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"862506ea003bfa9d1b00b7c2b0aaee4d78d96b68","tid":2118824,"uid":270220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"邊71個共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"定係佢地有tiktok AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b7c5f4482f57e